title: The End of an Era! The Final folklore Rankings!
description:
We wrap up the folklore era by giving our final folklore rankings! How does it compare to our initial ones?
And the big reveal.... the leaked footage of that lost lakes TikTok.
What did we miss? What's your rankings? And who is ready for Midnights?! Join us for our festivities live on TikTok and Instagram- @the13Podcast. If you're in the DFW area this weekend, join us Saturday at the Texican Court in Irving. You can find the details to that on our socials.
